import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Exam01 from "./components/web1908/exam/Exam01.vue"
import Exam02 from "./components/web1908/exam/Exam02.vue"
import Exam03 from "./components/web1908/exam/Exam03.vue"
import Fa04 from "./components/web1908/exam/Fa04.vue"
import Sub05 from "./components/web1908/exam/Sub05.vue"
import Exam06 from "./components/web1908/exam/Exam06.vue"
Vue.use(Router)
export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/Exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/Exam02',component:Exam02},
    {path:'/Exam03',component:Exam03},
    {path:'/Fa04',component:Fa04},
    {path:'/Sub05',component:Sub05},
    {path:'/Exam06',component:Exam06},
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer}
  ]
})
// http://127.0.0.1:8080/#/Exam01
